org.apache.flink.runtime.fs.maprfs

类 MapRFileSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.core.fs.FileSystem
      • org.apache.flink.runtime.fs.hdfs.HadoopFileSystem
        • org.apache.flink.runtime.fs.maprfs.MapRFileSystem

  • public class MapRFileSystem
extends HadoopFileSystem
    A MapR file system client for Flink.

    Internally, this class wraps the FileSystem implementation of the MapR file system client.
